---
title: Mushroom and Cheddar Burger with BBQ Onions, Wedges and Tomato Salad
description: This delicious Mushroom and Cheddar Burger has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-and-cheddar-burger-ba300538-8037f31a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/mushroom-and-cheddar-burger-615ac43c3e955b15806b97b5-c021588e.pdf
